# task_105_13_calendar_scheduling — Zoom-only design.
#
# All three keys are REQUIRED. install.sh fails fast if any of them are
# empty (no Jitsi fallback). The executor receives all three as env
# vars and must self-configure ~/.cli-anything-zoom/{config,tokens}.json
# from them — install.sh deliberately wipes that directory after using
# the credentials to reset the test account to zero meetings.
#
# To populate ZOOM_REFRESH_TOKEN see the "Zoom OAuth bootstrap" section
# in /tmp/clawbench_user_actions.md (one-time browser-based OAuth flow
# performed locally, refresh_token is long-lived).
ZOOM_CLIENT_ID
ZOOM_CLIENT_SECRET
ZOOM_REFRESH_TOKEN
